title: Javier Roca
text: Javier Leopoldo Roca Sepúlveda (born August 9, 1977 in <a href="Santiago">Santiago</a>) is a <a href="Chile">Chile</a>an professional <a href="association%20football">football</a> coach and former player who is currently head coach of <a href="Liga%201%20%28Indonesia%29">Liga 1</a> club <a href="Persik%20Kediri">Persik Kediri</a>.
